STATE
v.
Mohammed N. JILANI 149P17-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 5, 2018 Mohammed Nasser Jilani, for Jilani, Mohammed N. N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 9th of February 2018 by Defendant for Writ of Prohibition:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th of April 2018."
